# Balapan, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Balapan (Bashkir and ) is a rural locality (a village) in Matrayevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Balapan is located 58 km east of Zilair (the district's administrative centre) by road. Matrayevo is the nearest rural locality.
